Quickstrike:





Quickstrike walked over to a table in the CR room and sat up on it, 
with his legs dangling over the edge. He turned his head to Venomous, 
shrugging. "Who?"

Suddenly, he turned his head to the doorway of the room, just missing 
Black Arachnia leave the room. He shook his head. Now he was getting 
into the habit of missing her when he wanted to talk to her. He 
glowered.
